OL,5, The soaring cost of energy has hit     
OL,6, crisis point and more help is needed   
OL,7, for struggling households, Martin Lewis
OL,8, has told the BBC.                      
OL,10,FAnalysts have forecast the price of    
OL,11,Fbills will rise even further to nearly 
OL,12,F#4,000 a year for a typical home.      
OL,14,FIt comes as energy firms Shell and     
OL,15,FBritish Gas owner Centrica reported big
OL,16,Fincreases in profits after price hikes.
OL,18,FMoney expert Mr Lewis said people were 
OL,19,Fpanicking, warning "it will be         
OL,20,Fdesperate" when bills rise this winter.
